1.	Cacti Monitoring
A.	Install cacti on wsc-i-shizuoka
 
(중간에 DB root계정 비밀번호 설정 해야 함)

B.	Install snmpd on wsc-d-abudhabi
 

C.	Configure /etc/snmp/snmpd.conf on wsc-d-abudhabi and restart service
 

D.	Configure cacti on wsc-d-helsinki using firefox ( url : http://wsc-i-shizuoka.wsc17.cloud/cacti / default user : admin(DB 패스워드 따라옴) )
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
2.	Ping Monitoring
A.	Install package on wsc-i-shizuoka
 
 

B.	Configure /etc/nagios-plugins/config/ping.cfg
 

C.	Create /etc/icinga/objects/icmp_icinga.cfg
 

D.	Configure /etc/icinga/command.cfg
 

E.	Configure /etc/icinga/objects/contacts_icinga.conf
 

F.	Configure /etc/icinga/objects/generic-host_icinga.cfg
 

